    desc:"A simple, nourishing rice and moong dal porridge with cumin seeds — the base of the Ekadashi dinner.",
    ingredients:["1 cup rice","¼ cup green gram (moong dal)","5 cups water","1 tsp cumin seeds","Salt to taste"],
