    ingredients:["1¼ cups sago, large-sized, washed well, soaked overnight","10–12 French beans, stringed, finely chopped","1 carrot, medium, peeled, grated","1 potato, medium, peeled, chopped into bite-sized pieces","¼ cup groundnuts, roasted, coarsely ground","2-inch piece coconut (optional), fresh, grated","1 tbsp lemon juice","Fresh coriander leaves as desired","Salt to taste","For seasoning: 2 tbsp oil, 1 tsp mustard seeds, 1 tsp cumin seeds, 10–12 curry leaves, 1 tsp turmeric powder"],
